definitions.definition: A village in Welford parish, West Berkshire district, Berkshire , England ( OS grid ref SU3971 ) .
A village and civil parish (served by Wickham and Knowle Parish Council) in Winchester district, Hampshire , England ( OS grid ref SU5711 ) .
A habitational surname from Old English .
